    <item>
      <title>马克龙旨在敲定向乌克兰派遣教员的联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/macron-aims-to-finalize-coalition-to-send-instructors-to-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，他计划在未来几天组建一个联盟，派遣军事教官前往乌克兰，因为基辅需要训练数万名新士兵以击退俄罗斯的入侵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/macron-aims-to-finalize-coalition-to-send-instructors-to-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 19:16:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北约在遭遇阻力后缩减对乌克兰援助计划的雄心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/nato-scales-back-road-map-for-ukraine-aid-plan-after-pushback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，北约秘书长斯托尔滕贝格因面临北约成员国的反对而放弃了为乌克兰设立五年期军事援助基金的计划，而是要求各国维持目前的捐助额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/nato-scales-back-road-map-for-ukraine-aid-plan-after-pushback</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 19:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普盟友贝森特称耶伦利用岗位帮助拜登竞选 2024 年总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/trump-ally-bessent-says-yellen-using-post-to-aid-biden-2024-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Key Square Group LP 创始人、著名唐纳德·特朗普筹款人斯科特·贝森特 (Scott Bessent) 严厉批评了财政部长珍妮特·耶伦 (Janet Yellen)，指责她在大选前利用财政部刺激经济，以支持总统乔·拜登。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/trump-ally-bessent-says-yellen-using-post-to-aid-biden-2024-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 18:30:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党批准英国选举承诺 - 但工会反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/labour-approves-uk-election-pledges-but-one-union-objects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，工党在周五举行的党内和工会官员关键会议上签署了选举宣言——但未能赢得英国工党下属最大工会之一 Unite 的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/labour-approves-uk-election-pledges-but-one-union-objects</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 18:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
